text: Denise Christensen is a diver from Tucson, Arizona, United States. She won a gold medal in springboard diving at the 1979 Pan American Games in San Juan. In 1980 she became AIAW diving champion in springboard, and in 1982 she won the AIAW team championship with the Texas Longhorns. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:American female divers Category:Texas Longhorns women's swimmers Category:Sportspeople from Tucson, Arizona Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for the United States Category:Pan American Games medalists in diving Category:Divers at the 1979 Pan American Games
